OL,3,CSouth West hospitals among UK's worst
OL,4,Cfor ambulance handovers
OL,6,FFour of the UK's worst-ranking
OL,7,Fhospitals for ambulance handovers are
OL,8,Fbased in the South West.
OL,10,FTruro's Royal Cornwall Hospital,
OL,11,FSwindon's Great Western Hospitals, the
OL,12,FRoyal United Hospitals in Bath and
OL,13,FUniversity Hospitals Plymouth top the
OL,14,Flist for delays of more than 30
OL,15,Fminutes.
OL,17,FThe data - published by NHS England -
OL,18,Franked NHS trusts by the highest
OL,19,Fpercentage of ambulance handovers
OL,20,Flonger than 30 minutes in the week
OL,21,Fending 5 January.
