OL,9,FA&E teams.
OL,11,FSouth West NHS hospitals on the list:
OL,13,FIt reads, from left to right: name of
OL,14,FNHS trust, total number of handovers
OL,15,Fwhere time was known, number of
OL,16,Fhandovers longer than 30 minutes,
OL,17,Fpercentage of handovers longer than 30
OL,18,Fminutes.
