OL,3,CSouth West hospitals among UK's worst
OL,4,Cfor ambulance handovers
OL,6,FIt comes after a number of NHS
OL,7,Fhospitals in the South West -
OL,8,Fincluding the Royal Cornwall Hospital,
OL,9,FDerriford Hospital and Gloucestershire
OL,10,FRoyal Hospital - declared critical
OL,11,Fincidents.
OL,13,FWhile some of these have since been
OL,14,Fstood down, hospitals across the
OL,15,Fregion continue to experience high
OL,16,Flevels of flu, norovirus and other
OL,17,Frespiratory illnesses.
