OL,3,CSouth West hospitals among UK's worst
OL,4,Cfor ambulance handovers
OL,6,FIn response, staff, patients and
OL,7,Fvisitors to Southmead Hospital's
OL,8,Femergency wards are being asked to
OL,9,Fwear face masks as a temporary measure.
OL,11,F'Here to look after patients that
OL,12,Fabsolutely needed' - Chief Nursing
OL,13,FOfficer
OL,15,FProfessor Steve Hams, who is the Chief
OL,16,FNursing Officer for North Bristol NHS
OL,17,FTrust, said they are effectively
OL,18,Foperating a "one patient out, one
OL,19,Fpatient in" policy.
