OL,3,CSouth West hospitals among UK's worst
OL,4,Cfor ambulance handovers
OL,6,F"We're at full capacity here at
OL,7,FSouthmead," he told ITV News West
OL,8,FCountry.
OL,10,F"We do our best to ensure we balance
OL,11,Fthat the best we can. Of course we
OL,12,Fwant to ensure all patients that come
OL,13,Fto us are treated brilliantly and with
OL,14,Freal care and attention but it's a bit
OL,15,Fof a challenge."
OL,17,FProf Hams urged patients to only
OL,18,Fconsider going to hospital in an
OL,19,Femergency "if you really need to".
