OL,3,CSouth West hospitals among UK's worst
OL,4,Cfor ambulance handovers
OL,6,FHe said: "The best thing to do if
OL,7,Fyou're worried about an urgent care
OL,8,Fneed is to phone or look online for
OL,9,FNHS 111.
OL,11,F"The pharmacies in Bristol and
OL,12,Fsurrounding areas are brilliant and
OL,13,Fwill offer lots and lots of support.
OL,15,F"But, of course, if you are poorly or
OL,16,Fyou're worried about somebody, we will
OL,17,Falways be here to look after patients
OL,18,Fthat absolutely need it.
